snippet.title: [Second Galaxy] First Official Trailer (Open-World MMO Sci-Fi Adventure is coming to mobile!)
snippet.description:
Pre-registration has now officially begun! The Closed Beta Test is coming on July 5, and details of this test will be heading your way next week! 

App Store Pre-order: https://apple.co/2xc2NNI
Official Pre-registration Page: http://bit.ly/2xgzh9w
Official Website: https://secondgalaxy.zlongame.com
Google Play Store Pre-registration will open soon!

Brace yourselves, Commanders – the star gate is about to open!
We’ll see you soon, amid the sea of stars! A New Galaxy Awaits!

**Follow Us On**
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/Rw89w2v
Official Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SecondGalaxyM/
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/second_galaxy
Official Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/secondgalax...
Official YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfruRgqmhyGGgfzyErcckmg
